Another for causing menstruation. Take 1 ounce of nettle seeds and 1 dram each of myrrh and mastic. Make everything into fine powder and give it with grape must or white wine to drink. It makes menstruation return rapidly.

Another for causing menstruation. Take seed of masseroni , seed of yellow violet and also the true yellow violet, making everything into powder. Incorporate 2 scruples of saffron well. Then give it to drink with broth or white wine several times and you will see that it brings out the menstrual material.

Another for causing menstruation. Take 1 ounce of yeast, 1 ounce of peony root, Â½ ounce of madder, ordinary oil that is old and 2 scruples of saffron and mix everything and make it warm and give it to the sick one to drink in the evening and soon the menstruation will come.

